    </p>
</div><div class="tabs">
    <ul class="tabs">            <li class="sel"><span class="name-variation"><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear – Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Overview</bdi></a></span></li>            <li><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a/releases" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Releases</bdi></a></li>            <li><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a/recordings" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Recordings</bdi></a></li>            <li><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a/works" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Works</bdi></a></li>            <li><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a/events" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Events</bdi></a></li>            <li><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a/relationships" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Relationships</bdi></a></li>            <li><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a/aliases" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Aliases</bdi></a></li>            <li><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a/tags" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Tags</bdi></a></li>            <li><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a/details" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Details</bdi></a></li>            <li><a href="/artist/7b9f7611-5e31-49bc-921f-48754ad8991a/edit" title="Madisen Ward and the Mama Bear"><bdi>Edit</bdi></a></li>    </ul>
